 be aware of our mortality—but that reality shouldn’t govern all of our plans in life.</p><p>— Tom</p><hr><p><i>Katherine Hu contributed to this newsletter.</i></p><p><em>When you buy a book using a link in this newsletter, we receive a commission. Thank you for supporting </em>The Atlantic<em>.</em></p>